streams.schema:
type post @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: d1595bee-6f29-4760-b072-566fc6553201 | post") {
  modelVersion: String! @string(maxLength: 100)
  text: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  images: [String] @list(maxLength: 10000000) @string(maxLength: 2000000)
  videos: [String] @list(maxLength: 10000000) @string(maxLength: 2000000)
  options: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  encrypted: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}

type profile @createModel(accountRelation: SINGLE, description: "Dataverse: d1595bee-6f29-4760-b072-566fc6553201 | profile") {
  author: DID! @documentAccount
  version: CommitID! @documentVersion
  name: String! @string(maxLength: 100)
  description: String! @string(maxLength: 10000)
  image: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  background: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
}

type actionFile @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: d1595bee-6f29-4760-b072-566fc6553201 | ActionFile") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  action: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  relationId: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  fileName: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  fileType: Int!
  accessControl: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  deleted: Boolean
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}

type contentFolder @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: d1595bee-6f29-4760-b072-566fc6553201 | ContentFolder") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  indexFolderId: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  mirrorFileIds: [String!] @list(minLength: 0, maxLength: 300000000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  encryptedFileKeys: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}

type indexFile @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: d1595bee-6f29-4760-b072-566fc6553201 | IndexFile") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  contentId: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  contentType: String! @string(maxLength: 1000)
  fileName: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  fileType: Int!
  accessControl: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  deleted: Boolean
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}

type indexFolder @createModel(accountRelation: LIST, description: "Dataverse: d1595bee-6f29-4760-b072-566fc6553201 | IndexFolder") {
  fsVersion: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  folderName: String! @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  folderType: Int!
  contentFolderIds: [String!]! @list(minLength: 1, maxLength: 10000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  accessControl: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  parentFolderId: String @string(maxLength: 1000)
  childFolderIds: [String] @list(maxLength: 10000) @string(maxLength: 2000)
  createdAt: DateTime!
  updatedAt: DateTime!
  deleted: Boolean
  options: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
  reserved: String @string(maxLength: 300000000)
}
